description: Maintenance men Jimmy and Tony have been summoned to boss Victoria's office to answer the many complaints against them - which include secretly taking photos of women in the locker room. She is prepared to fire them but they beg for their jobs, so she gives them a choice - to keep their jobs, they must amuse her and do everything she says. The miscreant janitors agree and soon find themselves stripping naked, while Victoria makes Jimmy worship Tony's dirty feet and suck his dick in several positions, all the while showering them with a steady stream of verbal humiliation. And she's just getting started! (Part 1 of 2)
title: Very Bad Maintenance (Part 1 of 2)
